OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate
OL,6,Fsunshine this evening but quickly
OL,7,Fturning rather chilly. The rest of the
OL,8,Fnight will be dry and largely clear
OL,9,Fleading to a frost for many.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSome sunshine and a frost
OL,12,Ffirst thing in the morning for many.
OL,13,FThe rest of the day will then be dry,
OL,14,Fbright with best of sun along east
OL,15,Fcoast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FBright but with good deal of cloud
OL,19,Faround during this period and a few
OL,20,Fscattered showers. Rather breezy at
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
